These are the currently managed mirrors of the official [CodeRepository repository]:

 - [[Codeberg|codeberg.org]] - Needs a codeberg.org or gitlab.com or github.com account
 - [[GiteaCom|gitea.com]] - Can use OpenID for login
 - [[GitLab|gitlab.com]] - Needs a gitlab.com or github.com account
 - [[GitHub|github.com]] - Needs a github.com account
